N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 9650.10 - Severability

State Regulations

If any provision of these rules and regulations or the
application thereof to any person or circumstances is adjudged invalid by a
court of competent jurisdiction, such determination shall not affect or impair
the validity of the other provisions of these rules and regulations or the
application thereof to other persons and circumstances. Notes
